\begin_inset Formula $P(X_{i_{1}},X_{i_{2}},X_{i_{3}}|\mathbf{X_{j}=x_{j}^{(t-1)}},j\in\{1,\dots,n\}\backslash\{i_{1},i_{2},i_{3}\})$
\end_inset

